    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/be35e6423f51e4073303c386cf0d427f.webp?t=1767209252\" width=88 height=15 /></span><br>    Harness the unique skills of each character! Net gems and relocate them, or smash through layers of gems. Maybe you want to crush your opponents' gems by dropping balls on them. Or perhaps you’d like to torment your opponent instead by turning their gems black and white for a few turns. The choice is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/e5bd7a32027022a327e0fd7724d82993.webp?t=1767209252\" width=137 height=15 /></span><br>    As you play each stage, everything changes. The visuals evolve, as well as the music. An icy excavation site floods with lava, a dystopian Tokyo grows murky with fog, and a scrapyard in space comes to life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/2e7427ffda246818af37aff9083b8c32.poster.avif?t=1767209252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/2e7427ffda246818af37aff9083b8c32.webm?t=1767209252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/2e7427ffda246818af37aff9083b8c32.mp4?t=1767209252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/2fd33d10ad11b4b18dc7bac1f8e3f6db.webp?t=1767209252\" width=108 height=15 /></span><br>    Break friendships with your preferred character, or make new enemies in online matchmaking.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/c1c85616f37e6d8bc8952180af25197d.webp?t=1767209252\" width=125 height=15 /></span><br>    Choose your favorite character, from a bad-mannered witch with even worse-mannered hair, an electronic life form with reality warping powers, or a split-personality, teetering between beast and bot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858390/extras/3e064893a13c178010c844198b8e3c40.webp?t=1767209252\" width=102 height=15 /></span>",
